== 制作 ==
[[File:Elmo_kills_Murray.JPG|thumb]]放映时，这段镜头受到审查。]]

奥古斯塔·简·埃文斯（{{lang|en|Augusta Jane Evans}}）于1866年出版的《圣埃尔默》（{{lang|en|''St. Elmo''}}）是19世纪最畅销的小说之一，其销量起初仅次于《[[汤姆叔叔的小屋|汤姆叔叔的小屋]]》<ref name="Maurice">{{cite journal | author-last = Maurice | author-first = Arthur Bartlett. | title = 'Best Sellers' of Yesterday: I—Augusta Jane Evans's 'St. Elmo' | journal = The Bookman | volume = 31 | issue = 1 | year = 1910 | pages = 35–42}}</ref>，之后再被《[[宾虚：基督故事|宾虚：基督故事]]》（{{lang|en|''Ben-Hur: A Tale of the Christ''}}）超越<ref name="Fidler-2002">{{cite book | author-last = Fidler | author-first = William Perry | title = Augusta Evans Wilson, 1835–1909 | publisher = University of Alabama Press | year = 2002 | isbn = 978-0-8173-5026-0}}</ref>{{rp|129}}。小说的成功还带来广泛的文化影响，许多消费产品、酒店、汽船、火车车厢，甚至多个小镇都是以书名命，还有许多人用书中人物为孩子起名<ref name="Maurice" /><ref name="Fidler-2002" />{{rp|128–129}}。虽然有相当多的人表示有意把小说改编成戏剧作品，但埃文斯担心小说的主题在舞台上的呈现可能会存在扭曲，所以直到1909年才首次批准《圣埃尔默》的剧本。埃文斯于这年下半年去世后，小说的另外多个版本舞台剧作迅速面世，其中许多都取得了商业成功。<ref name="Fidler-2002" />{{rp|142–143}}此后不久，这个故事便被搬上银幕。1910年，《[[圣埃尔默_(1910年短片)|圣埃尔默]]》成为[[比豪泽公司|比豪泽公司]]制作的第2部电影，[[维塔格拉夫制片厂|维塔格拉夫制片厂]]制作的版本也在同年面世，两者均为单卷[[短片|短片]]。<ref name="Slide-1978">{{cite book | author-last = Slide | author-first = Anthony | title = Aspects of American Film History Prior to 1920 | url = https://archive.org/details/aspectsofamerica0000slid | publisher = Scarecrow Press | year = 1978 | isbn = 978-0-8108-1130-0 | page = [https://archive.org/details/aspectsofamerica0000slid/page/70 70]}}</ref><ref name="Slide-Gevinson-1987">{{cite book | author1-last = Slide | author1-first = Anthony | author2-last = Gevinson | author2-first = Alan | title = The Big V: A History of the Vitagraph Company | edition = revised | publisher = Scarecrow Press | isbn = 978-0-8108-2030-2 | year = 1987 | page = 195}}</ref>

1914年，正在巴尔博亚娱乐制片公司工作的威廉·乔西编写出《圣埃尔默》的第一部[[长篇_(电影术语)|电影长片]]改编剧本<ref name="MPW1676">{{cite journal | title = Doings at Los Angeles | journal = The Moving Picture World | volume = 20 | issue = 12 | date = 1914-06-20 | page = 1676 | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | url = https://archive.org/stream/movingpicturewor20newy#page/1676/mode/1up}}</ref>。电影拍摄在巴尔博亚公司的所在地<ref name="LAT">{{cite web | title = The movie capital of yore | website = Los Angeles Times | archivedate = 2013-10-16 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2009/oct/25/local/me-then25 | date = 2009-10-25 | author-last = Harvey | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131016045329/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/oct/25/local/me-then25 | author-first = Steve | accessdate = 2015-05-02 }}</ref>，[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[长滩_(加利福尼亚州)|长滩]]展开<ref name="MPN70">{{cite journal | author-last = Michell | author-first = A. Danson | title = St. Elmo | journal = Motion Picture News | volume = 10 | issue = 1 | date = 1914-07-11 | page = 70 | url = https://archive.org/stream/motionpicturenew101unse#page/n75/mode/1up | accessdate = 2015-05-02}}</ref>。制片公司所在地的街道对面当时正有教堂在建，工作人员拍摄了一段镜头，将之用于表现片中圣埃尔默建造教堂的情节<ref name="MPW1676" />。与电影同时代的多位作家记载本片的导演是伯特伦·布莱肯（{{lang|en|Bertram Bracken}}）<ref name="Justice-Smith-1914">{{cite book | editor1-last = Justice | editor1-first = Fred C. | editor2-last = Smith | editor2-first = Tom R. | title = Who's Who in the Film World | publisher = Film World Publishing | year = 1914 | oclc = 8807170 | url = http://archive.org/stream/whoswhoinfilmwor00just#page/28/mode/1up | page = 28}}</ref><ref name="BB52">{{cite journal | title = Bracken Back with Balboa Co. | journal = Billboard | volume = 26 | issue = 48 | date = 1914-11-28 | page = 52}}</ref>，包括[[美国电影学会|美国电影学会]]在内的部分现代来源也持同样看法<ref name="AFI">{{cite web | title = St. Elmo | work = Catalogue of Feature Films | publisher = American Film Institute | url = http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/DetailView.aspx?s=1&Movie=16398 | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402113341/http://www.afi.com/members/catalog/DetailView.aspx?s=1&Movie=16398 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-04-02 }}</ref>。但也有部分来源认为《圣埃尔默》是{{lang|en|J}}·戈登·爱德华兹（{{lang|en|J. Gordon Edwards}}）的导演处女作<ref name="LOC">{{cite web | title = St. Elmo [motion picture] | work = American Silent Feature Film Database | publisher = Library of Congress | date = 2014-03-31 | accessdate = 2015-01-09 | url = http://lcweb2.loc.gov:8081/diglib/ihas/loc.mbrs.sfdb.9500/default.html | archive-date = 2019-06-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190626140925/http://lcweb2.loc.gov:8081/diglib/ihas/loc.mbrs.sfdb.9500/default.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Goble-1999">{{cite book | author-last = Goble | author-first = Alan | title = The Complete Index to Literary Sources in Film | publisher = Bowker-Saur | year = 1999 | isbn = 978-1-85739-229-6 | page = 504}}</ref><ref name="Keister-2011">{{cite book | author-last = Keister | author-first = Douglas | title = Stories in Stone New York: A Field Guide to New York City Cemeteries and Their Residents | publisher = Gibbs Smith | year = 2011 | isbn = 978-1-4236-2102-7 | page = 91}}</ref>。两人之后都作为导演在福克斯影业工作了很长时间<ref name="Solomon-2011">{{cite book | author-last = Solomon | author-first = Aubrey | title = The Fox Film Corporation, 1915–1935: A History and Filmography | publisher = McFarland | year = 2011 | isbn = 978-0-7864-6286-5}}</ref>{{rp|14}}。

巴尔博亚公司在为影片宣传时强调其制作价值和艺术性<ref name="Atlanta">{{cite newspaper | title = At the Grand | newspaper = The Atlanta Constitution | date = 1914-10-04 | volume = 47 | issue = 111 | page = 14M | url = http://www.newspapers.com/image/26823027/ | subscription = yes | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | archive-date = 2018-09-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180916093133/https://www.newspapers.com/image/26823027/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，[[电影海报|电影海报]]上宣称片中有“194个绚烂的镜头”<ref name="Poster">{{cite web | title = ST. ELMO / [poster] ; J. Gordon Edwards ; 1914. | publisher = Margaret Herrick Library | url = http://catalog.oscars.org/vwebv/holdingsInfo?bibId=27965 | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | archive-date = 2019-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190305002413/http://catalog.oscars.org/vwebv/holdingsInfo?bibId=27965 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。但巴尔博亚并不是电影发行公司<ref name="Solomon-2011" />{{rp|13}}，所以他们于1914年5月同威廉·福克斯（{{lang|en|William Fox}}）的票房景点公司取得联系，请福克斯发行巴尔博亚制作的所有电影<ref name="Slide-2001">{{cite book | author-last = Slide | author-first = Anthony | title = The New Historical Dictionary of the American Film Industry | url = https://archive.org/details/newhistoricaldic0000slid | edition = 2nd | publisher = Scarecrow Press | isbn = 978-1-57886-015-9 | year = 2001 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/newhistoricaldic0000slid/page/26 26]–27}}</ref>，其中第一部便是《圣埃尔默》<ref name="Contracts">{{cite journal | title = Fox Contracts for Whole Balboa Output | journal = Motion Picture News | volume = 9 | issue = 20 | date = 1914-05-23 | page = 30 | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | url = http://www.archive.org/stream/motionp09moti#page/n583/mode/1up}}</ref>。所有影片的胶片拷贝可以在福克斯旗下的电影院放映，也可以通过所谓的州权发行系统转租给其他影院业主<ref name="Neale-Hall-2010">{{cite book | author1-last = Neale | author1-first = Steve | author2-last = Hall | author2-first = Sheldon | title = Epics, Spectacles, and Blockbusters: A Hollywood History | url = https://archive.org/details/epicsspectaclesb0000hall | publisher = Wayne State University Press | year = 2010 | isbn = 978-0-8143-3008-1 | page = [https://archive.org/details/epicsspectaclesb0000hall/page/24 24]}}</ref>。1915年2月1日，威廉·福克斯注册成立福克斯影业，票房景点公司的资产也转入新公司名下<ref name="Solomon-2011" />{{rp|19}}。票房景点的部分影片继续由福克斯影业发行，《圣埃尔默》便是其中一部<ref name="Fox">{{cite journal | title = Fox Film Company Formed in Milwaukee | journal = Motion Picture News | volume = 10 | issue = 21 | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | date = 1914-11-28 | page = 33 | url = http://www.archive.org/stream/motionpicturenew102unse#page/n622/mode/1up/}}</ref>，该片在部分地区一直放映到了1916年<ref name="Honolulu">{{cite newspaper | title = 'St. Elmo' to be Film Feature at New Playhouse | newspaper = Honolulu Star-Bulletin | volume = 23 | issue = 7425 | date = 1916-01-29 | page = 7 | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | url = http://www.newspapers.com/image/85833017/ | subscription = yes | archive-date = 2018-09-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180916093131/https://www.newspapers.com/image/85833017/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 反响和影响 ==
[[File:St_Elmo_drinks_with_the_devil.jpg|thumb]]

电影上映同期所获评价褒贬不一。{{lang|en|A}}·丹森·米歇尔在《电影新闻》（{{lang|en|''Motion Picture News''}}）撰文称赞本片比小说的改编舞台剧作更为出色，并特别赞扬了片中的摄影表现<ref name="MPN70" />。《电影世界》（{{lang|en|''Moving Picture World''}}）的汉福德·贾德森（{{lang|en|Hanford Judson}}）也对电影有较好的的总体评价，他认为片中虽然有少数镜头略显“做作”，但本片的制作品质以及剧情的吸引力足以弥补这些缺陷<ref name="MPW70">{{cite journal | author-last = Judson | author-first = Hanford C. | title = St. Elmo | journal = The Moving Picture World | volume = 21 | issue = 1 | date = 1914-07-04 | page = 70 | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | url = https://archive.org/stream/movingpicturewor21newy#page/70/mode/1up}}</ref>。不过，《电影画报》（{{lang|en|''Movie Pictorial''}}）的凡德海登·法尔斯（{{lang|en|Vanderheyden Fyles}}）认为片中长滩等地的风景镜头对剧情无关紧要，而且这个经过改编的故事也“混乱得（让人）莫名其妙”<ref name="MP28">{{cite journal | author-last = Fyles | author-first = Vanderheyden | title = Famous Feature Films | journal = Movie Pictorial | volume = 1 | issue = 20 | date = 1914-09-19 | url = https://archive.org/stream/MoviePictorialSept.-nov.1914/MoviePictorialSept-Nov1914#page/n98/mode/1up | page = 28 | accessdate = 2015-05-02}}</ref>。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》上刊登的一篇评论将本片批评得体无全肤，称电影毁掉了原著小说，很可能会让制片商血本无归<ref name="Variety17">{{cite journal | title = St. Elmo | journal = Variety | volume = 35 | issue = 13 | date = 1914-09-28 | page = 17 | url = https://archive.org/stream/variety35-1914-08#page/n116/mode/1up | accessdate = 2015-05-02}}</ref>。芝加哥审查委员会认为片中部分镜头令人反感，因此要求电影在该市上映时要去除这些内容，其中包括哈蒙德和默里的决斗，以及默里的尸首<ref name="Menace">{{cite journal | title = Growing Menace of Chicago Censors: More Films Cut | journal = Motography | volume = 12 | issue = 14 | date = 1914-11-03 | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | url = https://archive.org/stream/motography12elec#page/458/mode/1up | pages = 459–462}}</ref>。

虽然评价褒贬不一，但《圣埃尔默》获得了商业上的成功<ref name="Jura-Bardin-2007" />{{rp|204}}，据《电影演员周刊》（{{lang|en|''The Photoplayers' Weekly''}}）报道，影片创下了新的票房纪录<ref name="TPW">{{cite journal | title = Balboa's Phenomenal Success in the Film World | journal = The Photoplayers' Weekly | volume = 3 | issue = 21 | date = 1915-12-25 | page = 3 | accessdate = 2015-05-02 | url = https://archive.org/stream/ThePhotoplayersWeeklySept.1915ToMarch1916/PhotoplayersWeeklySept1915-Mar1916#page/n70/mode/1up/}}</ref>。次年，伯特伦·布莱肯为巴尔博亚公司制作了另一部根据奥古斯塔·简·埃文斯同名小说改编的电影《比尤拉》，该片无论是在原著小说还是剧情上都和《圣埃尔默》没有直接关联<ref name="Fidler-2002" />{{rp|56, 125}}，但在市场宣传中还是自称为《圣埃尔默》的续集<ref name="BB52" /><ref name="Jura-Bardin-2007" />{{rp|204}}。1923年，福克斯影业再次将小说《圣埃尔默》搬上银幕，并且片名也没有改，该片同样获得了成功<ref name="Fidler-2002" />{{rp|144}}。

如今，巴尔博亚娱乐制片公司制作的电影中有约90%已经佚失<ref name="LAT" />，1914年的《圣埃尔默》很可能也不例外<ref name=Tarbox-1983>{{cite book | author-last = Tarbox | author-first = Charles H. | title = Lost Films 1895–1917 | publisher = Jef Films | year = 1983 | isbn = 978-0-9610916-0-6 | pages = 188, 191}}</ref>。从[[国会图书馆_(美国)|美国国会图书馆]]的记载来看，本片已经没有任何现存副本<ref name="LOC" />。

